This is the game called "The Golden Bell"

Cach choi:

1. Dang nhap
2. Co the tao phong hoac xin tham gia vao phong (bang cach double click vao ten phong do)
3. Khi tao phong:

- Se hien thi nhung nguoi choi xin vao phong ra 1 danh sach, co the double click vao ten de tu choi hoac cho phep vao phong
- Khi an start se bat dau tro choi

4. Khi bat dau choi:

- Se co 20 giay de suy nghi chon dap an moi cau hoi
- Tra loi sai coi nhu thua, tra loi dung duoc chuyen sang cau tiep theo
